      <title>越南咖啡出口紧张局面将持续至年底</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/crucial-coffee-exports-from-vietnam-to-be-tight-through-year-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南是世界上最大的罗布斯塔咖啡种植国，其咖啡出口很可能在年底前保持紧张，给2024年已上涨近三分之二的价格带来更大压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/crucial-coffee-exports-from-vietnam-to-be-tight-through-year-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 07:30:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奢侈品行业困境、北欧银行业绩低迷：欧洲、中东和非洲地区本周业绩展望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/luxury-woes-nordic-bank-blues-emea-earnings-week-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着财报季的到来，卡地亚母公司历峰集团 (Richemont SA) 和风衣制造商博柏利 (Burberry Plc) 下周公布财报时，将面临与去年同期相比的挑战。对于这两家公司来说，去年第一财季恰逢中国解封，在当年晚些时候需求下滑之前，它们实现了增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/luxury-woes-nordic-bank-blues-emea-earnings-week-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
